WEBVTT

00:00:19.189 --> 00:00:24.729
ikh, ROZA BIELIAUSKIENĖ. haynt, dem tsvantsikstn oktober,

00:00:24.764 --> 00:00:26.094
toyznt nayn hundert

00:00:26.159 --> 00:00:27.780
zeks un zekhtsikstn yor,

00:00:27.593 --> 00:00:29.233
zeks un nayntsikstn.

00:00:29.333 --> 00:00:31.463
oy, zeks un nayntsikstn yor.

00:00:31.513 --> 00:00:35.213
nem ikh a intervyu bay Fanyen BRANCOVSKAYA.

00:00:35.213 --> 00:00:39.283
Vilne, Lite. di shprakh, yidish.

00:00:44.581 --> 00:00:48.950
ikh, Fanye BRANCOVSKAYA Yokheles,

00:00:48.950 --> 00:00:53.035
bin geborn gevorn dem tsvey un tsvantsikstn may,

00:00:53.035 --> 00:00:56.192
toyznt nayn hundert tsvey un tsvantsikstn yor,

00:00:56.192 --> 00:00:57.569
in Kovne.

00:00:57.705 --> 00:01:00.368
mir iz fir un zibetsik yor.

00:01:02.160 --> 00:01:06.147
mayn, der, di, ikh gedenk

00:01:06.147 --> 00:01:10.540
vegn mayne z- zeydns, bobes fun beyde tsdodim,

00:01:10.540 --> 00:01:12.500
i funem tsad fun der muter,

00:01:12.500 --> 00:01:14.653
i fun tsad fun foter.

00:01:15.183 --> 00:01:20.716
mayne kroyvim, der zeyde mit der boben fun mame's tsad,

00:01:20.716 --> 00:01:23.755
zaynen fun VARĖNA, fun Aran.

00:01:23.978 --> 00:01:27.991
zey zayne-, nu, di muter iz dortn geborn gevorn

00:01:27.991 --> 00:01:31.212
in toyznt nayn hundert ershtn yor.

00:01:31.382 --> 00:01:33.278
vi hot men ir gerufn?

00:01:33.343 --> 00:01:35.540
mayn muter hot men gerufn Rokhl.

00:01:35.540 --> 00:01:37.798
RACHEL ⟨oyf⟩ men ir gerufn.

00:01:37.798 --> 00:01:41.538
ir familye di meydlshe iz geven GALUNSKI,

00:01:41.538 --> 00:01:44.109
nor, de- mi-, ven zi hot khasene gehat,

00:01:44.137 --> 00:01:46.877
di eltern mayne hobn khasene gehat

00:01:46.877 --> 00:01:51.527
dem tsvey un tsvantsikstn IYUL', eyn un tsvantsikstn yor.

00:01:53.160 --> 00:01:59.173
di bo- der zeyde mayner hot gearbet in Aran.

00:01:59.173 --> 00:02:01.874
fun onheyb hot er gearbet oyf a

00:02:01.874 --> 00:02:04.510
oyf a pi-, oyf a papir-fabrik.

00:02:04.900 --> 00:02:08.640
gelebt hobn zey in der Oran velkhe hot gehert tsu Lite.

00:02:08.640 --> 00:02:11.043
Oran iz tseteylt oyf tsvey teyln:

00:02:11.043 --> 00:02:15.173
di Meretshanke, s'hot tset-, eyn helft iz di poylishe teyl,

00:02:15.173 --> 00:02:18.095
dortn vu s'iz der, ban geyt durkh.

00:02:18.235 --> 00:02:19.572
di tsveyte teyl,

00:02:19.572 --> 00:02:23.260
dos iz di vu es geyt di sh-, di alte Oran,

00:02:23.260 --> 00:02:27.090
dortn hot gelebt der bobe mayner mitn zeydn, mit di boben.

00:02:27.090 --> 00:02:30.118
dem zeydn hot men gerufn Bentsien.

00:02:31.184 --> 00:02:33.807
di boben hot men gerufn Khane-Leye.

00:02:34.940 --> 00:02:38.229
mayn muter hot gehat a groyse mishpokhe.

00:02:38.229 --> 00:02:41.718
tsum glik zaynen zey ale

00:02:42.829 --> 00:02:46.740
nit durkhgelebt di okupatsye-tsaytn.

00:02:47.673 --> 00:02:51.118
der zey- di zeyd-, der zeyde mit der boben

00:02:52.166 --> 00:02:55.588
hobn gelebt in a sht- in a hoyz,

00:02:55.611 --> 00:02:57.966
vu es iz g-, vu hot zikh gefunen

00:02:57.966 --> 00:03:03.540
der yidisher bank. dos iz geven, der bank hot mit zikh forgeshtelt in tsimer,

00:03:03.540 --> 00:03:10.099
un dortn hot gelebt bay zey der forshteyer, der, fun bank,

00:03:10.099 --> 00:03:13.077
er hot bay zey gelebt, er hot bay zey gegesn,

00:03:13.077 --> 00:03:16.144
un un er hot dortn gearbet.

00:03:18.058 --> 00:03:19.369
di muter,

00:03:20.524 --> 00:03:22.724
ven ikh bin geborn gevorn,

00:03:22.724 --> 00:03:27.391
iz na- ven mir iz geven a yor iz di muter nit gezunt, krank gevorn.

00:03:27.391 --> 00:03:33.347
un zi hot mir mitn zey- mitn foter avekgefirt tsu der boben mitn zeydn.

00:03:34.218 --> 00:03:41.173
di gantse tsayt flegt mir der bobe mitn zeydn bavayzn di fotografye fun mayne eltern un ⟨dos⟩ zogn, az dos iz

00:03:41.173 --> 00:03:43.062
der foter un dos iz di muter.

00:03:43.106 --> 00:03:46.551
ven di muter iz tsu mir gekumen mir opnemen

00:03:46.551 --> 00:03:48.818
hob ikh ir nit gevelt onerkenen,

00:03:48.818 --> 00:03:53.907
vayl ikh hob geshlept di bilder un ikh hob geshribn PAPA, MAMA ⟨bum⟩.

00:03:53.907 --> 00:03:59.462
⟨azoy az⟩ zey zaynen in albom. dos iz geven, in shtub flegt men es bay undz dertseyln.

00:04:02.077 --> 00:04:04.055
fun der muter's mishpokhe

00:04:04.055 --> 00:04:06.439
iz der eltster bruder

00:04:09.260 --> 00:04:11.694
GRISHA, Hirsh,

00:04:13.402 --> 00:04:15.366
geve- geven

00:04:16.422 --> 00:04:21.017
der am- in tsvantsikstn yor iz er geven der

00:04:21.017 --> 00:04:24.730
forshteyer fun Ratn-Farband in Lite.

00:04:24.730 --> 00:04:26.811
un dortn bay im

00:04:26.811 --> 00:04:29.550
hobn zikh bakent mayn foter mit der muter.

00:04:32.010 --> 00:04:36.205
er iz geshtorbn in zibn un draysikstn yor,

00:04:36.205 --> 00:04:40.938
rikhtiker in zeks un draysikstn yor. vegn dem hob ikh zi-, hobn mir zikh dervust

00:04:40.938 --> 00:04:44.871
in a tsaytung f- vos iz geven aroysgegebn in Vilne.

00:04:44.871 --> 00:04:49.027
tsum glik iz er geshtorbn mit a natureler toyt,

00:04:49.036 --> 00:04:54.320
un nit gevorn dershosn, voyle- vayle vi a diplomatisher arbeter

00:04:54.320 --> 00:04:59.102
in Ratn-Farband, velkher hot khuts Lite gearbet in Triest,

00:04:59.102 --> 00:05:02.927
volt men im zikher umgebrakht. er hot bavizn tsu shtarbn.

00:05:02.927 --> 00:05:06.971
zayn froy un di kinder veys ikh nit vu zey zaynen.

00:05:08.238 --> 00:05:15.104
di gantse mishpokhe der muter's, khuts eyn bruder, zaynen aribergeforn in Yisroel.

00:05:15.838 --> 00:05:19.740
fun onheyb iz, der eltster bruder, Dov,

00:05:19.740 --> 00:05:24.250
Berl, iz aribergeforn in fir un tsvantsikstn yor.

00:05:24.821 --> 00:05:26.288
un er hot,

00:05:26.288 --> 00:05:28.666
tsu im zaynen gekumen tsu forn

00:05:28.666 --> 00:05:30.955
di shvester, Shifre,

00:05:30.955 --> 00:05:33.155
zaynen gekumen tsu forn tsu im

00:05:33.155 --> 00:05:36.177
di bobe m- mitn zeydn,

00:05:37.032 --> 00:05:41.454
s'iz gekumen tsu forn nakher nokh tsvey brider,

00:05:41.454 --> 00:05:45.765
 Mot- der yi-, Yitskhok un Motl, der yingster.

00:05:45.884 --> 00:05:50.617
eyner fun di brider iz geblibn in Tavrik, in TAURAGĖ,

00:05:50.617 --> 00:05:53.373
mit a groyser mishpokhe hot er gehat.

00:05:53.373 --> 00:05:55.995
er hot gehat zeks kinder.

00:05:55.995 --> 00:06:00.084
ober zeyer goyrl iz shoyn an anderer.

00:06:00.403 --> 00:06:04.581
er iz antlo-, ven s'hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome iz er antlofn

00:06:04.581 --> 00:06:09.270
fun Tavrik, er iz gegangen mit di yingste tokhter

00:06:09.270 --> 00:06:12.314
iz geven krank, iz er gegangen tsum dokter,

00:06:12.314 --> 00:06:16.336
ven er hot zikh umgekert hot men im gezogt az di froy mit di kinder

00:06:16.336 --> 00:06:18.936
zaynen a-, hobn zikh evakuirt.

00:06:18.936 --> 00:06:22.050
vayle dortn in Tavrik, dos iz geven hart bay der grenets.

00:06:22.358 --> 00:06:24.447
er iz avekgeforn,

00:06:24.743 --> 00:06:27.232
derforn biz Rige. in Rige hot men

00:06:27.232 --> 00:06:32.876
zey gezogt az er hot zikh umgekert in Tavrik. zey hobn zikh umgekert, er mit der yingster,

00:06:32.876 --> 00:06:34.121
Shulamis,

00:06:34.121 --> 00:06:36.409
zaynen ave- hobn zikh evakuirt,

00:06:36.409 --> 00:06:38.832
un geven in Uzbekistan.

00:06:38.832 --> 00:06:40.165
un dos iz,

00:06:40.165 --> 00:06:42.890
er hot zikh geratevet un di yingste tokhter.

00:06:42.890 --> 00:06:45.409
di ga-, di mishpokhe, di froy mit di kinder

00:06:45.409 --> 00:06:47.550
zaynen umgekumen.

00:06:49.262 --> 00:06:51.239
zi kumt itster tsu forn

00:06:51.239 --> 00:06:55.951
shoyn etlekhe mol, un in Tavrik oyf, geyt zi oyf keyver-oves.

00:06:58.297 --> 00:06:59.550
der,

00:07:00.875 --> 00:07:04.963
di mishpokhe, velkhe ikh hob ni- nit gehat mit zey keyn kontakt,

00:07:05.703 --> 00:07:09.444
hob ikh opgefunen shpeter. nu, ikh vel dos dertseyln mistome shpeter.

00:07:09.444 --> 00:07:13.258
dos iz di mishpokhe fun mayn muter.

00:07:13.258 --> 00:07:16.747
di muter iz umgekumen, vegn dem vel ikh ⟨vel⟩ dertseyln.

00:07:16.747 --> 00:07:18.947
dem foter's mishpokhe

00:07:18.947 --> 00:07:20.236
hot gelebt...

00:07:20.281 --> 00:07:23.147
vi hot men im gerufn? ir hot nokh im nit

00:07:23.147 --> 00:07:25.393
gezogt vi men hot gerufn ayer foter.

00:07:25.169 --> 00:07:28.310
ye, neyn, ikh vil nor zogn, ma- eyn moment, u- ay- un ikh vil

00:07:28.310 --> 00:07:33.600
zogn az di bobe's familye iz geven Oranski.

00:07:33.935 --> 00:07:37.913
di bobe's familye iz geven Oranski, un ir shvester

00:07:37.913 --> 00:07:43.646
iz umgekumen oykhet in Ponar. zey zaynen fun Li-, zi hot gelebt in Eyshishok,

00:07:43.646 --> 00:07:46.202
fun Eyshishok hot zi khasene gehat in Lite,

00:07:46.202 --> 00:07:51.557
un fun ⟨Li-⟩ zaynen zey antlofn in Vilne, un umgekumen mitn man mit a kind.

00:07:53.399 --> 00:07:55.954
mayn foter, Benyomen,

00:07:55.954 --> 00:08:02.866
ay, ikh hob nokh nit gezogt. di muter iz geborn gevorn in ershtn yor hob ikh gezogt, dem zekstn merts.

00:08:02.866 --> 00:08:07.154
der foter iz geborn gevorn in toyznt nayn hundert

00:08:07.154 --> 00:08:10.199
akht un nayntsikstn yor.

00:08:10.199 --> 00:08:12.421
dem finf un tsvantsikst-

00:08:10.411 --> 00:08:12.410
toyznt akht hundert.

00:08:12.421 --> 00:08:17.954
toyznt akht hundert akht un nayntsikstn yor, dem finf un tsvantsikstn september.

00:08:17.954 --> 00:08:20.377
der foter's mishpokhe,

00:08:20.464 --> 00:08:22.270
der zeyde mayner,

00:08:22.270 --> 00:08:23.648
Velvl,

00:08:23.692 --> 00:08:28.048
iz geborn gev- -vorn in Vilne, er iz a Vilner.

00:08:28.048 --> 00:08:32.024
di bobe iz a Sventsyaner, Gilinski.

00:08:32.024 --> 00:08:35.848
in Sventsyan iz geven a barimte mishpokhe, di Gilinskis.

00:08:35.936 --> 00:08:38.380
dem foter's shvesterkinder,

00:08:38.380 --> 00:08:41.269
zey hobn gelebt in in Sventsyan.

00:08:41.292 --> 00:08:45.270
der shvesterkind Motl Gilinski iz bakant

00:08:45.270 --> 00:08:48.079
vi der Batke. er hot gearbet

00:08:48.079 --> 00:08:49.910
in Medem-Sanatorye,

00:08:49.910 --> 00:08:51.346
o, ir hot gehert zikher vegn...

00:08:51.346 --> 00:08:56.501
er hot gearbet in Medem-Sanatorye, un gesh- ki- ongeshribn afile a opere far kinder,

00:08:56.523 --> 00:08:57.612
"Di Lyalkes".

00:08:57.612 --> 00:09:00.701
dos iz geven dem foter's shvesterkind.

00:09:00.723 --> 00:09:04.010
un di kinder hobn im gerufn der Batke, der foter.

00:09:04.679 --> 00:09:08.310
er iz umgekumen oykhet in Vilner geto.

00:09:09.057 --> 00:09:12.502
nu, ven ikh vel reydn vegn geto vel ikh efsher dertseyln.

00:09:13.205 --> 00:09:14.427
de-

00:09:14.427 --> 00:09:15.516
di,

00:09:15.516 --> 00:09:20.183
dem fo- di gan- dem foter's mishpokhe di gantse, khuts eyn bruder,

00:09:20.183 --> 00:09:25.880
velkher iz in fir un tsvantsikstn yor aribergeforn in Yisroel,

00:09:25.880 --> 00:09:28.660
di gantse mishpokhe iz umgekumen.

00:09:28.971 --> 00:09:30.905
der foter hot gehat

00:09:30.905 --> 00:09:34.105
de- der elter- der eltster bruder, Dovid,

00:09:34.105 --> 00:09:36.630
velkher hot gelebt in Kovne,

00:09:36.927 --> 00:09:43.194
er iz umgekumen mitn zun, Leyzer, un mit di tokhter, Feygele. mir zaynen geven

00:09:43.194 --> 00:09:49.170
dray shvesterkinder a nomen nokh eyn b- elter-boben, kentik.

00:09:49.170 --> 00:09:52.170
vayle in Kovne hot men gerufn Feygele,

00:09:52.215 --> 00:09:57.215
in, mir hot men, mikh, mir hobn geredt ki- ven ikh bin geven a kind hobn mir geredt rusish,

00:09:57.215 --> 00:09:59.482
hob, iz mayn nomen iz geven Fanye.

00:09:59.526 --> 00:10:03.977
kh'hob a shvesterkind in Yisroel vos iz geblibn lebn, zi iz TSIPORA.

00:10:04.537 --> 00:10:08.710
zi iz fun fir un tsvantsikstn yor. yederer der zelber nomen,

00:10:08.070 --> 00:10:08.997
nomen.

00:10:08.710 --> 00:10:09.890
ob- andersh.

00:10:11.293 --> 00:10:13.515
dem foter's,

00:10:14.727 --> 00:10:21.260
der broy- der, eyn bruder iz geven in Yisroel, Dovid iz umgekumen in Kovne,

00:10:22.303 --> 00:10:27.658
di ga- di g- er hot gehat nokh dray brider,

00:10:27.864 --> 00:10:31.797
nokh tsvey brider, vayle zey zaynen dray, dos iz geven Hirsh

00:10:31.797 --> 00:10:33.553
un Moyshe, der yingster.

00:10:33.553 --> 00:10:35.508
zey zaynen geven dray shv- f-,

00:10:35.508 --> 00:10:37.019
fir shvester,

00:10:37.019 --> 00:10:41.930
Ester, Teme, Etl un Zelde.

00:10:43.499 --> 00:10:50.099
zey zaynen ale umgekumen mit der gantser zeyer mishpokhe. ven ikh vel dertseyln vayter vel ikh zogn.

00:10:50.099 --> 00:10:54.210
vos gedenk ikh vegn mayne zeydes mit di b- mit di bobes?

00:10:54.210 --> 00:11:00.321
bay der bobe, in Kovne, mitn zeydn, bin ikh geven in,

00:11:01.930 --> 00:11:04.920
gekumen tsu forn in

00:11:04.920 --> 00:11:08.443
fir, dray un draysikstn, fir un draysikstn yor.

00:11:08.443 --> 00:11:09.540
es iz geven

00:11:09.540 --> 00:11:13.265
d- a a opmakh tsvishn Poyln un Lite

00:11:13.332 --> 00:11:16.709
az der vos hot gehat erd in Poyln

00:11:16.709 --> 00:11:17.887
bay der grenets

00:11:17.887 --> 00:11:22.700
hot gekent geyn baarbetn di erd oyfn tog in Poyln.

00:11:22.700 --> 00:11:27.957
ver s'hot gehat erd in Lite hot gekent in meshekh fun tog,

00:11:28.335 --> 00:11:30.668
biz vanen es iz likhtik,

00:11:30.668 --> 00:11:36.002
baarbetn di erd in Lite, nor zikh umkern tsurik in Poyln un

00:11:36.002 --> 00:11:38.357
zikh umkern tsurik in Lite.

00:11:38.357 --> 00:11:40.646
di ma- di muter mayne,

00:11:41.050 --> 00:11:44.361
me hot eydes gezogt az zi hot gehat erd dortn,

00:11:44.361 --> 00:11:47.027
vegn velkhe ikh hob nit, mir hobn nit gevust,

00:11:47.250 --> 00:11:51.383
un di m- di muter hot mir, mit mayn shvesterl,

00:11:51.383 --> 00:11:54.716
mit, un zi zaynen gekumen tsu forn in Aran,

00:11:54.716 --> 00:11:56.050
in litvishe Aran.

00:11:56.094 --> 00:11:59.850
azoy vi di, mir zaynen geven nokh kinder,

00:11:59.850 --> 00:12:04.250
ikh bin geven fun tsvey un tsvantsikstn yor, di shvesterl fun zibn un tsvantsikstn,

00:12:04.355 --> 00:12:08.488
hot men undz erloybt tsu nekhtikn bay der boben

00:12:08.510 --> 00:12:10.021
mitn zeydn.

00:12:10.021 --> 00:12:12.799
di bobe hot zikh zeyer gegreyt tsu undzer kumen.

00:12:12.850 --> 00:12:17.977
zi hot pozemkes far zey, zi hot spetsyel gehat a tsig kedey undz tsu

00:12:17.977 --> 00:12:21.999
 gebn tsig, zi, m'hot gehaltn az fun tsigene milkh

00:12:21.999 --> 00:12:24.621
iz zeyer gezunt far di kinder.

00:12:24.778 --> 00:12:29.511
ikh geven in Ko- in dortn, in Kov- in v- Aran,

00:12:29.511 --> 00:12:35.445
un oyf, nokh di milkhome hob ikh afile getrofn eyne a froy,

00:12:35.445 --> 00:12:40.622
velkhe hot zikh zeyer baleydikt vos ikh hob ir nit derkent. ikh bin geven gekumen a- vi a gast, hot zi mir...

00:12:40.622 --> 00:12:43.200
ikh hob dortn organizirt afile a teater

00:12:43.200 --> 00:12:44.845
in dem tsayt fun zumer.

00:12:44.845 --> 00:12:49.489
mir hobn forgeshtelt, geley- Sholem-Aleykhemen, geley- -redt a, geleyent,

00:12:49.489 --> 00:12:51.445
un dos hot zi gedenkt.

00:12:51.445 --> 00:12:54.067
zi hot tsu mir sh- gehat sh- zeyer a sakh

00:12:54.067 --> 00:12:58.556
geven baleydikt vos ikh ikh ken ir ⟨nit⟩ un zi hot gehat pretenzyes tsu mir.

00:12:58.711 --> 00:13:01.334
in der tsayt ⟨oyb⟩ ven ikh bin geven,

00:13:01.334 --> 00:13:06.778
bin ikh avekgeforn mit ⟨dem o⟩ vos hot gearbet in bank,

00:13:06.778 --> 00:13:09.511
un vos iz geven der,

00:13:09.511 --> 00:13:12.022
gelebt bay mayn z- boben mitn zeydn,

00:13:12.022 --> 00:13:15.756
mit zey bin ikh, mit im bin ikh avekgeforn in Kovne,

00:13:15.756 --> 00:13:20.600
vayle in Kovne hot hot gelebt dem foter's bruder,

00:13:20.600 --> 00:13:23.378
un in der tsayt hobn tsvey brider gelebt,

00:13:23.544 --> 00:13:30.478
Yitskhok un Motl hobn gelebt dortn in, in Kovne.

00:13:30.752 --> 00:13:34.329
ikh bin geven, ikh hob zikh getrofn dortn oykhet mit mayne

00:13:34.329 --> 00:13:40.196
a khaverte, dos heyst, s'iz geven a di, a tokhter fun mayn muter's a khaverte,

00:13:40.196 --> 00:13:44.279
vayle, un mir, ikh bin dan geven a vokh tsayt in Kovne.

00:13:44.279 --> 00:13:48.396
dos iz bay mir geblibn vi a o- ondenk,

00:13:48.396 --> 00:13:49.760
vi a gedank.

00:13:49.770 --> 00:13:53.882
dos iz vegn... nakher zaynen mayne zeyde un bobe avekgeforn in

00:13:53.904 --> 00:13:56.830
Yisroel, ober ikh bin shoyn nit geforn zikh gezegenen,

00:13:56.830 --> 00:13:59.860
gezegenen zikh iz geforn di muter aleyn.

00:13:59.860 --> 00:14:01.650
zi hot gehat a g- UNK.

00:14:01.650 --> 00:14:04.349
di muter hot zeyer gut gekent litvish,

00:14:04.349 --> 00:14:09.482
un derfar vos zi hot gekent litvish hobn di litvishe grenets-militer

00:14:09.482 --> 00:14:15.571
erloybt, ikh, mir zoln zikh, mir zoln, di kinder zoln dortn blaybn nekhtikn.

00:14:17.440 --> 00:14:22.974
azoy az mir hobn ge- geganvet di grenets, vi me flegt es zogn in yidish.

00:14:24.263 --> 00:14:27.196
der zeyde mayner fun Vilne

00:14:27.849 --> 00:14:30.338
iz geven a malyer. ober er iz geven a

00:14:30.427 --> 00:14:35.649
a a, nit keyn poshet-, a kunst-malyer, er hot, me hot im ge- in Vilne gekent.

00:14:37.464 --> 00:14:39.819
di feters mayn-

00:14:39.819 --> 00:14:42.686
di bo-, dem zeyde, dos iz geven Velvl,

00:14:42.686 --> 00:14:46.708
di s- di bobe iz geven Sore-Gisye,

00:14:48.716 --> 00:14:50.893
zeyer a voyle froy.

00:14:50.893 --> 00:14:54.427
mayn zeyde iz geven a,

00:14:54.427 --> 00:14:56.960
er hot gelebt oyf Antokol,

00:14:57.281 --> 00:15:00.992
dem numer vey- ken ikh aykh nit zogn, nor dortn vu s'iz itster

00:15:01.014 --> 00:15:03.192
di apteyk ⟨LABDARA⟩.

00:15:04.259 --> 00:15:08.790
dortn hobn mir gelebt. dortn iz geven a groyser gortn,

00:15:09.237 --> 00:15:11.970
un mir flegn kumen forn tsum zeydn.

00:15:12.997 --> 00:15:15.060
der bild vos

00:15:15.060 --> 00:15:19.664
ikh vel aykh shpeter vayzn fun der gim-, fun der mishpokhe fun nayn un draysikstn yor,

00:15:19.664 --> 00:15:22.464
iz oykh gemakht dortn oyfn hoyf,

00:15:22.464 --> 00:15:24.775
oyf Antokol.

00:15:26.963 --> 00:15:29.874
tsum zeydn flegn mir forn

00:15:29.874 --> 00:15:34.674
mit a droshke, mit a v-, mit a ferd un vogn, vayle mir hobn gelebt

00:15:35.052 --> 00:15:38.297
dan oyf Zavalne, ikh vel ⟨no-⟩ dertseyln vegn alts.

00:15:38.297 --> 00:15:44.132
un, mir flegn forn, s'iz geven a gantser,

00:15:44.132 --> 00:15:47.132
a gantse UNK flegn forn tsum zeydn mitn boben.

00:15:48.258 --> 00:15:53.969
vi ikh hob aykh gezogt bin ikh geborn gevorn in Kovne

00:15:53.969 --> 00:15:56.636
in zibn un tsvantsikstn yor.

00:15:56.636 --> 00:16:04.680
der foter mayner hot nit gehat keyn litvishe birgershaft, hot zikh aroysgevizn.

00:16:04.726 --> 00:16:09.215
der foter hot in Ko-, der foter mayner iz geven a elektriker,

00:16:09.215 --> 00:16:13.504
er hot geendikt a fakh-shul in Daytshland,

00:16:13.526 --> 00:16:16.260
un in Daytshland hot er gearbet

00:16:16.726 --> 00:16:21.637
in tsayt fun der, far der milkh-, far der ershter velt-milkhome,

00:16:21.637 --> 00:16:25.971
un in der tsayt fun der ershter velt-, vi a oy- vi a elektriker

00:16:25.971 --> 00:16:27.682
in A.E.G.

00:16:27.755 --> 00:16:33.300
der dokument fun endikn zayn shul iz geven groys mistome vi der tish.

00:16:33.300 --> 00:16:36.610
geven a riziker dokument mit tseykhenungen farsheydene.

00:16:36.610 --> 00:16:40.080
dan flegt men aroysgebn azoyne dokumentn.

00:16:39.593 --> 00:16:41.882
un vos iz dos A.E.G.?

00:16:41.526 --> 00:16:49.571
dos iz Algemeyne Elektrishe Gezelshaft. dos iz a bakante daytshishe gezelshaft velkhe dukht zikh biz itster nokh, ⟨dem⟩.

00:16:49.571 --> 00:16:52.015
oyf yedn fal in der tsayt fun milkhome

00:16:52.422 --> 00:16:56.778
hobn, iz ge-, in, fun der tsveyter velt-milkhome zaynen zey nokh geven.

00:16:57.622 --> 00:17:04.133
in Kovne hot mayn foter gearbet oyf der ayznban-elektrostantsye,

00:17:04.472 --> 00:17:05.961
vi a elektriker.

00:17:07.627 --> 00:17:10.116
gelebt hobn mir in Kovne

00:17:10.428 --> 00:17:13.694
vi ir hot zikh, vi me hot mir gezogt, in Shants.

00:17:14.862 --> 00:17:16.760
vayl dos iz geven noent

00:17:16.760 --> 00:17:20.817
fun der grenets, vayl dor-, nokh der milkhome hob ikh getrofn

00:17:20.817 --> 00:17:23.600
mayne a khaverte un ir mishpokhe,

00:17:23.600 --> 00:17:26.017
dos iz di mishpokhe Galpern,

00:17:26.721 --> 00:17:28.121
velkhe

00:17:28.121 --> 00:17:33.521
hobn, zey hobn mir oykhet vegn dem dertseylt, vos a d- a m- a a

00:17:33.521 --> 00:17:40.476
shtrikh fun mayn, fun di v- ershte dermonungen fun kindheyt.

00:17:40.527 --> 00:17:42.438
s'iz arayngegangen,

00:17:42.438 --> 00:17:44.860
mir zaynen geven in vald

00:17:44.860 --> 00:17:47.900
un in mayne hor hot a bin

00:17:47.900 --> 00:17:50.483
zikh araynge⟨trogn⟩, di m- di muter

00:17:50.483 --> 00:17:53.416
un di froy Galpern hobn zikh zeyer dershrokn,

00:17:53.416 --> 00:17:56.772
di bin zol mir nit a bis ton, hot men genumen

00:17:56.772 --> 00:18:02.883
tsvey mm shern, un me hot mir ongehoybn shern, mit sherlekh, m'hot mir ongehoybn shern di hor,

00:18:03.083 --> 00:18:07.394
un ikh hob a fotografye vi ikh bin in gantsn opgegolt,

00:18:07.840 --> 00:18:08.540
vayle

00:18:08.540 --> 00:18:12.728
di hor iz iz, z- kedey, vayl di bin zol mir nit far⟨UNK⟩.

00:18:12.728 --> 00:18:14.705
a tsveyte zakh,

00:18:14.705 --> 00:18:18.061
mayn foter hot gehat zeyer a raykhe biblyotek.

00:18:18.986 --> 00:18:22.452
er hot zikh gelernt unter

00:18:22.452 --> 00:18:25.964
un- unter ⟨oygn⟩ hot er zikh gelernt vi an inzhenyer,

00:18:26.412 --> 00:18:28.820
un er hot gehat zeyer a sakh bikher.

00:18:28.820 --> 00:18:33.635
ikh hob bashlosn optsugebn, aroystsushlepn di bikher,

00:18:34.300 --> 00:18:37.780
un ver s'iz farbaygegangen hob ikh gegebn di bikher.

00:18:38.652 --> 00:18:44.963
 de- dos iz, ge- di shkheynim hobn dos derzen, un zey hobn oyfgenumen ale bikher un gebrakht in shtub.

00:18:44.963 --> 00:18:47.363
kh'hob bashlosn az me darf tseteyln.

00:18:47.363 --> 00:18:48.785
a tsveytn mol,

00:18:48.830 --> 00:18:52.596
nu, di muter hot mir avekgesh-, di muter hot geshvangert, dos iz geven

00:18:52.596 --> 00:18:54.863
in zibn un tsvantsikstn yor,

00:18:55.018 --> 00:18:58.818
ven, eyder s'iz geborn gevorn mayn shvesterl,

00:18:58.818 --> 00:19:03.510
di muter hot mir avekgeshikt tsu di o mishpokhe Galpern,

00:19:03.510 --> 00:19:05.885
zeyer zeyde hot gehat a krom,

00:19:05.885 --> 00:19:07.107
nokh apelsin.

00:19:07.152 --> 00:19:12.900
ikh hob oyfn veg tse- tseteylt di gantse APEL'SINY un gekumen in shtub, un di mame hot nit gekent farshteyn

00:19:12.900 --> 00:19:16.974
far vos Galperns hobn nit gegebn mir keyn APEL'SINY, zi vet dokh batsoln.

00:19:17.157 --> 00:19:20.150
ot ot azoyne shtrikhn, dos iz geblibn.

00:19:21.180 --> 00:19:25.512
mayn shvesterl iz geborn gevorn dem draytsetn may,

00:19:25.512 --> 00:19:27.579
zibn un tsvantsikstn yor.

00:19:28.947 --> 00:19:33.791
zi hot, n-, ven di shvesterl iz geborn gevorn hot men mayn foter arestirt.

00:19:35.651 --> 00:19:39.917
un di bobe iz geven gekumen fun Aran

00:19:39.917 --> 00:19:42.340
kedey tsu helfn di muter.

00:19:42.340 --> 00:19:45.406
ikh bin gekumen tsu der muter

00:19:45.406 --> 00:19:47.517
tsu, tsu gast,

00:19:47.517 --> 00:19:52.162
ongeton nit vi, nit vi mayn muter hot, volt gehaltn far neytik.

00:19:52.162 --> 00:19:56.628
ikh bin geven epes ongeton in dem vos ikh bin arumgegangen oyfn hoyf.

00:19:56.805 --> 00:19:59.049
di boben iz nit geven in kop

00:19:59.072 --> 00:20:06.894
mir tsu, tsu iberton, vayl dem foter hot men arestirt. dos iz geven nokh der

00:20:06.894 --> 00:20:11.827
Smetonas-iberkerenish in zibn un, in, tsulib dem iz es geven.

00:20:12.923 --> 00:20:19.380
di muter hot gefregt, far vos bin ikh azoy ongeton?

00:20:19.380 --> 00:20:22.160
hot di bobe derklert, az ikh bin,

00:20:22.160 --> 00:20:24.278
az ⟨d- az⟩ foter iz avekgeforn

00:20:24.278 --> 00:20:28.879
ergets vu hot zikh opgeshtelt a elektrostantsye, az er iz geven a guter spetsyalist,

00:20:28.879 --> 00:20:30.968
hot men mir dan avekgefirt

00:20:31.082 --> 00:20:33.704
o, yo, hot er mitgenumen di shlislen.

00:20:33.704 --> 00:20:39.148
un derfar hot zi nit gekent efenen dem almer kedey mir tsu,

00:20:40.640 --> 00:20:43.637
kedey mir tsu iberton.

00:20:43.637 --> 00:20:45.682
dos iz azoyne, dermonen.

00:20:45.916 --> 00:20:49.560
azoy vi der foter iz geven a poylisher birger,

00:20:49.560 --> 00:20:52.783
hot men im mishpetn nit gekent,

00:20:52.783 --> 00:20:55.656
hot men undz aribergeshikt in Vilne.

00:20:55.656 --> 00:20:58.411
s'iz geblibn bay mir in zikorn

00:20:58.411 --> 00:21:01.878
vi mir forn in a fur iber a taykh.

00:21:01.878 --> 00:21:05.234
vos far a taykhl, dos iz geven mistome nit keyn shtark

00:21:05.234 --> 00:21:09.700
groyser vayl mir zaynen aribergeforn mitn fur, un i-

00:21:09.700 --> 00:21:13.820
bay mir in zikorn fun, vi a kind iz geblibn der fur,

00:21:13.820 --> 00:21:16.630
der forn oyfn fur, un di vaser.

00:21:17.991 --> 00:21:20.124
mir zaynen gekumen in Vilne.

00:21:20.124 --> 00:21:22.324
in Vilne hot men gebetn

00:21:22.511 --> 00:21:25.340
di, bay der muter tsu batsoln,

00:21:25.340 --> 00:21:29.013
t- gelt tsu batsoln, di muter hot bahaltn di gelt un zi hot

00:21:29.203 --> 00:21:34.048
zikh nit oryentirt in di pray- nokh ⟨haltn⟩ batsolt di gevise sume gelt,

00:21:34.048 --> 00:21:39.492
un undz hot men arib- aroysgelozn. mir, mi- mir hobn, mir zaynen gekumen tsum zeydn,

00:21:39.492 --> 00:21:40.892
oyf Antokol,

00:21:40.892 --> 00:21:45.203
ober glaykh nokh dem hobn mir genumen a dire

00:21:45.203 --> 00:21:46.070
oyf

00:21:46.070 --> 00:21:51.136
Pohulan-, Groys-Pohulanke. dos iz oyf BASANAVIČIUS itst-, oyf Groys-Pohulanke.

00:21:51.136 --> 00:21:57.244
di hoyz vu es hot gelebt antkegn, di ershte hoyz hintern teater,

00:21:57.838 --> 00:22:01.793
dortn ho- in in a,

00:22:02.571 --> 00:22:07.793
in a di- in a, in dem zelbe hoyz hot in zayner tsayt gelebt Shabad.

00:22:09.080 --> 00:22:14.502
vos s'iz mir geblibn fun der dire, ikh hob, ikh hob, ikh bin krank gevorn oyf skarlatin.

00:22:15.591 --> 00:22:20.391
di muter mayne hot bashlosn az dos iz mozlen,

00:22:20.391 --> 00:22:23.414
un zi hot arayngeleygt tsu mir in bet

00:22:23.414 --> 00:22:25.280
di yingere shvester

00:22:25.280 --> 00:22:28.915
kedey ⟨az⟩ beyde kinder zoln shoyn mozlen tsuzamen.

00:22:28.915 --> 00:22:30.093
eyn glik

00:22:30.093 --> 00:22:34.582
vos di k-, di muter hot mit der brust gekormet mayn shvesterl,

00:22:34.582 --> 00:22:38.693
un t- kinder vos me kormet mit brust zaynen n-,

00:22:38.790 --> 00:22:41.160
hob- hobn, hobn nit ongenumen di infektsye.

00:22:41.160 --> 00:22:45.115
UNK hot zikh aroysge⟨UNK⟩ dos iz geven skarlatin.

00:22:45.423 --> 00:22:50.001
nokh dem zaynen mir aribergeforn oykh oyf Pohulanke,

00:22:50.001 --> 00:22:53.712
oyf, in tsvey ve- hoyfn vayter,

00:22:53.712 --> 00:22:57.868
dos iz geven a

00:22:58.498 --> 00:23:00.876
hoyz vos shteyt nokh itster,

00:23:00.876 --> 00:23:02.765
a a ey- eyn-gorndike, di,

00:23:02.832 --> 00:23:05.743
di hoyz iz a groyse, ober in hoyf eyn-gorndike,

00:23:05.743 --> 00:23:08.520
dortn hobn mir oykh gelebt bay balebatim

00:23:08.841 --> 00:23:10.130
in a tsimer.

00:23:10.320 --> 00:23:14.641
der foter hot glaykh, vi mir zaynen gekumen in Vilne,

00:23:14.641 --> 00:23:18.463
ongehoybn arbetn in yidishn tekhnikum vi a instruktor.

00:23:18.503 --> 00:23:21.140
in der tsayt iz nokh der yidisher tea-

00:23:21.140 --> 00:23:23.414
tekhnikum geven

00:23:23.414 --> 00:23:25.125
oyf rog Pohulanke,

00:23:25.125 --> 00:23:29.970
un itster ALGIRDO, dos iz PIŁSUDSKIEGO, oyf yenem ort hot zikh gefunen.

00:23:29.970 --> 00:23:31.614
shpeter iz der t-

00:23:31.614 --> 00:23:33.970
der tekhnikum aribergeforn

00:23:33.970 --> 00:23:37.681
oyf Gdanske, itster ruft zikh dos di gas...

00:23:37.902 --> 00:23:39.657
ISLANDIJOS.

00:23:38.502 --> 00:23:39.902
ISLANDIJOS,

00:23:39.991 --> 00:23:44.168
un er hot gearbet fun zibn un tsvantsikstn yor

00:23:44.168 --> 00:23:47.191
biz onheyb fun der milkhome.

00:23:47.191 --> 00:23:50.880
bizn letstn tog hot er gearbet in tekhnikum.

00:23:50.880 --> 00:23:52.679
in tekhnikum hot er gearbet

00:23:52.702 --> 00:23:55.346
vi a instruktor-elektrotekhniker.

00:23:55.346 --> 00:23:59.657
ikh hob bilder fun de- yener tsayt, vos me hot mir gefunen.

00:23:59.657 --> 00:24:01.100
khuts dem,

00:24:02.906 --> 00:24:05.729
di lage in tekhnikum iz geven zeyer a shvere.

00:24:05.729 --> 00:24:09.960
der Ort flegt zeyer veynik

00:24:09.960 --> 00:24:13.595
tso-, v- tsoln. me flegt zey farshraybn

00:24:13.595 --> 00:24:15.662
dos vos zey hobn fardint,

00:24:15.662 --> 00:24:17.773
flegt men farshraybn in bukh

00:24:17.773 --> 00:24:21.062
un aroystsoln minimaln gehalt.

00:24:23.327 --> 00:24:24.660
der

00:24:24.810 --> 00:24:30.000
der foter hot dan geefnt oyf Zavalne dray un draysik,

00:24:32.130 --> 00:24:36.794
dos iz itster finf un draysik, PYLIMO finf un draysik iz itster,

00:24:36.794 --> 00:24:40.571
geefnt a varshtat, a elektromekhanisher varshtat,

00:24:40.571 --> 00:24:44.060
velkher hot geklu- vos er hot zikh gerufn zeyer azoy

00:24:44.060 --> 00:24:45.970
⟨POMPYOZ⟩, DYNAMO.

00:24:46.470 --> 00:24:50.600
ikh hob oykh a fotografye fun, mit a shild fun der tsayt.

00:24:51.545 --> 00:24:56.256
khuts dem vos der foter hot geha-, dos iz geven nit keyn groyse dire,

00:24:56.256 --> 00:25:00.323
der un- a untershte dire tsulib dem mm varshtat.

00:25:00.400 --> 00:25:01.790
in der dire,

00:25:02.190 --> 00:25:07.212
der ershter tsimer, dos iz geven a de- der varshtat,

00:25:07.352 --> 00:25:11.685
opgeteylt iz geven dortn hobn geve- gesh- geshlofn mayne eltern,

00:25:11.685 --> 00:25:13.641
s'iz geven a ts- nokh a tsimer,

00:25:13.641 --> 00:25:16.574
opgeteylt zaynen mir gelebt mit der shvesterl,

00:25:16.574 --> 00:25:17.885
un a kikh.

00:25:17.885 --> 00:25:21.396
di k-, m'hot gekent arayngeyn i fun eyn zayt, i fun tsveytn.

00:25:21.418 --> 00:25:23.396
dortn iz itster,

00:25:23.463 --> 00:25:27.507
in eyn teyl fun dem iz a krom itster.

00:25:29.687 --> 00:25:34.754
mir zaynen gekumen in zibn un tsvantsikstn yor, in akht un tsvantsikstn yor,

00:25:34.754 --> 00:25:37.132
bin ikh avek lernen zikh,

00:25:37.132 --> 00:25:39.800
akht un tsvantsikstn, nayn un tsvantsikstn shul-yor,

00:25:39.800 --> 00:25:43.510
bin ikh zikh avek lernen in der Sofye Gurevitsh-gimnazye,

00:25:43.665 --> 00:25:46.520
velkhe hot zikh gefunen oyf Makove finf.

00:25:47.092 --> 00:25:48.848
di gimnazye iz nokh dan,

00:25:48.981 --> 00:25:51.250
ven ikh bin dan nokh ongekumen,

00:25:51.250 --> 00:25:54.730
iz nokh geven di farvalterin undzere,

00:25:54.730 --> 00:25:56.870
Sofye Markovne Gurevitsh.

00:25:56.870 --> 00:25:59.890
dos iz geven a oysergeveynlekher pedagog,

00:26:00.203 --> 00:26:02.759
di shul iz geven a private,

00:26:02.759 --> 00:26:07.781
un di lerer velkhe hobn bay undz gearbet in der shul,

00:26:07.811 --> 00:26:10.478
der, oyb nemen

00:26:10.478 --> 00:26:14.189
nor di reshime fun di lerer, bay undz hot gearbet

00:26:14.233 --> 00:26:18.240
di froy fun dokter Shabad, Stefanye Lvovne.

00:26:18.450 --> 00:26:19.989
bay undz hot gearbet

00:26:20.011 --> 00:26:21.833
di tokhter

00:26:21.833 --> 00:26:24.300
fun d- dokter Shabad,

00:26:24.322 --> 00:26:26.033
Regine Vaynraykh,

00:26:26.056 --> 00:26:30.060
di froy fun dem bavustn Va- Vaynraykh.

00:26:30.060 --> 00:26:31.771
bay undz hot gearbet,

00:26:31.771 --> 00:26:34.551
mayn ershte lererin iz geven

00:26:35.420 --> 00:26:37.810
Malke Khaimson.

00:26:37.810 --> 00:26:40.793
Khaimson, dos iz di froy fun Bastomski,

00:26:40.793 --> 00:26:43.815
velkhe hobn aroysgegebn di barimte

00:26:43.815 --> 00:26:47.860
kinder- -zhurnaln, "Di Grininke Beymelekh",

00:26:47.860 --> 00:26:50.771
un aroysgegebn dem "Khaver".

00:26:51.418 --> 00:26:52.996
dos zaynen geven undzere lerer.

00:26:53.107 --> 00:26:56.870
zeyer, s'iz geven nokh a sakh azoyne lerer. der lerer Rabinovitsh,

00:26:57.463 --> 00:27:00.490
vu s'iz bay undz geven a shul

00:27:00.490 --> 00:27:04.810
velkhe ven ikh hob nakher shoyn gearbet in shul,

00:27:04.810 --> 00:27:06.907
ven nakher ven, dos iz geven,

00:27:06.907 --> 00:27:10.218
velkhe hot undz gegebn a oysergeveynlekhe ertsiung.

00:27:10.218 --> 00:27:12.841
un dos iz bay undz geblibn

00:27:12.841 --> 00:27:15.729
in, bay un- in di blutn, vi me zogt dos.

00:27:15.729 --> 00:27:18.774
kh'el aykh gebn aza min bayshpil. me hot undz,

00:27:18.774 --> 00:27:22.352
mir hobn ge-, mir esn kez, mir esn puter,

00:27:22.352 --> 00:27:23.732
mir ve-, veys nit v-,

00:27:23.732 --> 00:27:27.298
di lererin hot bashtelt spetsyel

00:27:27.298 --> 00:27:29.798
bay undzer a foter...
